name kvsetkeys
category Package
revision 79461
shortdesc Key value parser with default handler support
longdesc This package provides \kvsetkeys, a variant of package keyval's
longdesc \setkeys. It allows the user to specify a handler that deals
longdesc with unknown options. Active commas and equal signs may be used
longdesc (e.g. see babel's shorthands) and only one level of curly
longdesc braces are removed from the values.
